Read a CSV file:

Name, EmpId, Designation
Jack, 15, Developer
Mary, 13, Designer
John, 12, Developer
Jane, 17, Designer
Johny, 19, Tester

Save into another file in the format:

Designers
Mary (EmpId: 13)
Jane (EmpId: 17)

Developers
John (EmpId: 12)
Jack (EmpId: 15)

Tester
Johny (EmpId: 19)

Listing should be in ascending order of Designation.
Designation should be plural if it has more than one Employee.